		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="730" width="500" height="116" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">深罪浸礼者依据自身元素核心顺序依次开出的元素护罩，其厚度为<span color="#ff9999">12火</span><span>/</span><span color="#7fbfff">12水</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffacff">8雷</span><span>/</span><span color="#99ffff">12冻</span><span>盾，击破使其短暂瘫痪3s。<br/></span><span color="#ffbfbf">(N5) </span><span>厚度变为</span><span color="#ff9999">18火</span><span>/</span><span color="#7fbfff">18水</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffacff">12雷</span><span>/</span><span color="#99ffff">18冻</span><span>盾，可伤害转化；元素护罩会尝试记录所受伤害，并在破盾之后造成</span><span color="#ffdfbf">50%记录伤害的普通伤害</span><span>，免疫与护罩属性相同的伤害。记录的伤害不超过</span><span color="#ffdfbf">25%浸礼者生命值</span><span>，即最终伤害不超过</span><span color="#ffdfbf">12.5%浸礼者生命值</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
